The paper discusses the maintenance of materialisations in datalog systems, which is a topic related to databases (cs.DB). The paper also proposes algorithms to optimize the maintenance process, which involves reasoning and inference (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the evaluation of rules, which is related to logic (cs.LO). The paper also involves the handling of data structures (cs.DS) and programming languages (cs.PL).
